find bandoneons in Argentina

00:53:04.080 --> 00:53:06.650
because most of them,
they are taken to Japan.

00:53:06.650 --> 00:53:09.310
In Japan, there are a
lot of bandoneon players.

00:53:09.310 --> 00:53:12.910
And in Europe, there are a lot
of bandoneon players as well.

00:53:12.910 --> 00:53:16.800
So there was a time that it was
very cheap to buy in Argentina.

00:53:16.800 --> 00:53:20.260
So most bandoneons were gone.

00:53:20.260 --> 00:53:23.390
But in those days, there
are many factories.

00:53:23.390 --> 00:53:26.710
There is a factory in Germany.

00:53:26.710 --> 00:53:29.810
The most famous one is
Double A, Alfred Arnold.

00:53:29.810 --> 00:53:31.680
And this is actually
a bandoneon from them,

00:53:31.680 --> 00:53:35.960
that they gave to
me as a sponsorship.

00:53:35.960 --> 00:53:39.690
And in Argentina, there
is another, Lucia,

00:53:39.690 --> 00:53:41.620
doing bandoneons now.

00:53:41.620 --> 00:53:42.890
He's really good.

00:53:42.890 --> 00:53:45.380
So in those days, if you
want to buy a bandoneon,

00:53:45.380 --> 00:53:49.630
