00:53:55.970 --> 00:53:59.970
The instrument was
invented in Germany.

00:53:59.970 --> 00:54:03.580
And it was invented to play
religious music at the church.

00:54:03.580 --> 00:54:08.880
And somehow, it ended up in
the cabarets in Argentina.

00:54:08.880 --> 00:54:12.347
